    {
      "scene_index": 5,
      "label": "第五场",
      "characters_present": [
        "白素贞",
        "青蛇"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（青蛇败上，白素贞追上，舞蹈。白素贞打青蛇抢背。四云旗、四风旗自两边分上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "白素贞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看剑。"
        },
        {
          "character": "青蛇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且慢，白蛇仙子果然道法非凡，望乞慈悲，饶恕于我，情愿跟随仙子，侍奉左"
        },
        {
          "character": "青蛇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "右，一同修炼，求得正果。我若口不应心，定遭五雷之劫。"
        },
        {
          "character": "白素贞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这……你既发誓，快快请起。"
        },
        {
          "character": "青蛇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢仙子慈悲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "白素贞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "青蛇仙翁，你可知阴阳有别，你我怎能一路同行?"
        },
        {
          "character": "青蛇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个，俺情愿化一女身，侍奉仙子终生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "白素贞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既然如此，就请仙翁变来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "青蛇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "献丑了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "青蛇",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "口念真言翻身变，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四风旗遮青蛇同下，遮青蛇化身同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "青蛇",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "变一个青春女婵娟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "青蛇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "白蛇仙子，你看我变得如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "白素贞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "果然法术高强。我有意与你结为姐妹，生死与共，不知你意如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "青蛇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正合我意，请问仙子道高几何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "白素贞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "七千九百余年。"
        },
        {
          "character": "青蛇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，仙子高我五百余载。"
        },
        {
          "character": "白素贞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此说来我占长了，你我对天一拜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "白素贞",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "数千年居山林修真养性，"
        },
        {
          "character": "青蛇",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "姐姐你道高我五百余春。"
        },
        {
          "character": "白素贞",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我与你肝胆相照患难与共，"
        },
        {
          "character": "青蛇",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "若三心和二意五雷轰身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "青蛇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姐姐请上，受小妹一拜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "白素贞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为姐也有一拜。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（白素贞、青蛇同拜。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "青蛇",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "从今后姐妹们相依相伴，"
        },
        {
          "character": "白素贞",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "同甘苦共患难永不离分。"
        },
        {
          "character": "青蛇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请姐姐到古洞观赏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "白素贞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正要拜观。"
        },
        {
          "character": "青蛇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众小仙，回洞去者。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "青蛇 （同沽美酒） 喜相逢，恰相逢，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "巧今朝得知音。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在山林拜昆仲。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "炼仙丹变化无穷。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "渡群灵扶助苍身。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "学慈航大显神通。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宏誓愿锦绣前程。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（急急风，众人同亮相。）"
        }
      ],
